text: Decent rice bowl and salad. Would be better in terms of quality if dont use instant fish and beef patty.

I ordered salad bowls from them several times on Deliveroo and Grab. They're named Green Monster Salad in these apps. They offer very good salad options at reasonable price: salmon, chicken, prawn, kale etc. The Twin Monsters deal is really worth it at $25 for 2 bowls of salad. Recommend!
